title: Daisy Kaitano
text: Daisy Kaitano (born 20 September 1993) is a Zimbabwean footballer. She represented Zimbabwe in the <a href="Football%20at%20the%202016%20Summer%20Olympics">football competition</a> at the <a href="Football%20at%20the%202016%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Women%27s%20tournament">2016 Summer Olympics</a>.
